# Project Repositories

This workspace contains two separate products (each with its own git repo):

| Product | Folders | Description |
|---------|---------|-------------|
| **TesboX** | `Tesbo-Backend/`, `Tesbo-Frontend/`, `Tesbo-Automation-Agents/` | Main platform — backend API, frontend UI, automation agents |
| **TesboX-Runner** | `Tesbo-Execution/` (separate git repo) | Standalone test execution service — API + Playwright workers |

## Deployment Topology

| Product | Component | Target | Workflow |
|---------|-----------|--------|----------|
| **TesboX** | Frontend | Droplet (80→3000) | `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` |
| **TesboX** | Backend | Droplet (80→7000) | `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` |
| **TesboX** | Automation Agent | Droplet (80→7400) | `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` |
| **TesboX-Runner** | Execution API | Droplet (80→7420) | `Tesbo-Execution/.github/workflows/deploy.yml` |
| **TesboX-Runner** | Execution Workers | DOKS K8s (KEDA autoscale) | `Tesbo-Execution/.github/workflows/deploy.yml` |

- All images stored in DigitalOcean Container Registry (DOCR).
- TesboX and TesboX-Runner are independent products with separate deploy pipelines.
- See `docs/deploy-guide.md` for secrets, setup, and verification steps.
